Name: aloe-django
Version: 0.0.4
Summary: Package for testing Django applications with Aloe
Home-page: https://github.com/koterpillar/aloe_django
Author: Alexey Kotlyarov
Author-email: a@koterpillar.com
License: UNKNOWN
Description: Aloe-Django
        -------------
        
        Utilities for using Aloe with Django:
        
        - A `harvest` command to run Gherkin tests
        - A collection of steps to aid in testing Django applications
        
        Aloe and Aloe-Django are based on [Lettuce](http://lettuce.it/).
        
